==English==

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-drizzle.ogg|Audio (US)}}
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪzəl|-ɪzəl]]

===Etymology===
The first part of the verb, ''driz-'' comes probably from Middle English ''drēse'', Old English ''[[drēosan]]''

===Verb===
{{en-verb|drizzl|ing}}

# To [[rain]] lightly

